      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay that makes sense. so if i'm the one indemnifying them, i'm basically saying if someone sues them because of something i did (like using an image i didn't have the rights to), i have to pay for their lawyers and anything they lose? it feels like i'm taking on a huge amount of risk for just one project.",
